def transform(in1):
    indices = tf.expand_dims(in1, axis=1)
    indices = tf.repeat(indices, 2, axis=1)
    values = tf.range(tf.reduce_max(indices) + 1)
    output = tf.gather(values, indices)
    return output

def transform(in1):

    return arr

def transform(in1):
    indices = tf.expand_dims(tf.range(tf.size(in1)), axis=1)
    indices = tf.tile(indices, [1, 2])
    pairs = tf.stack([in1, tf.argmax(indices, axis=1)], axis=1)
    return pairs
